<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <title>The Normies</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="./media/favicon/icon.png">
    <!--bootstrap-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.0.0/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-Gn5384xqQ1aoWXA+058RXPxPg6fy4IWvTNh0E263XmFcJlSAwiGgFAW/dAiS6JXm" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.2.1.slim.min.js" integrity="sha384-KJ3o2DKtIkvYIK3UENzmM7KCkRr/rE9/Qpg6aAZGJwFDMVNA/GpGFF93hXpG5KkN" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/popper.js/1.12.9/umd/popper.min.js" integrity="sha384-ApNbgh9B+Y1QKtv3Rn7W3mgPxhU9K/ScQsAP7hUibX39j7fakFPskvXusvfa0b4Q" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.0.0/js/bootstrap.min.js" integrity="sha384-JZR6Spejh4U02d8jOt6vLEHfe/JQGiRRSQQxSfFWpi1MquVdAyjUar5+76PVCmYl" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <!--google fonts-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Roboto+Slab">
    <!--custom css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./styles/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark bg-dark fixed-top">
            <button class="navbar-toggler navbar-toggler-right" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#myNavbar" aria-controls="myNavbar" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
                <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
            </button>
            <a class="navbar-brand" href="#">
                <img src="./media/nav/navbrand.png" width="40" height="40" class="d-inline-block align-top">
                The Normies
            </a>
                    
            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="myNavbar">
                <ul class="navbar-nav mr-auto mt-2 mt-md-0">
                    <li class="nav-item active">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="/">Home <span class="sr-only">(current)</span></a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="/clan">Our Clan</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="/about">About</a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </nav>
    </header>
    <!--<div class="container-fluid" id="home-slides">-->
        <div id="bannerSlides" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel" data-interval="5000" data-pause="false">
            <div class="carousel-inner" id="bannerInner"></div>
        </div>
    <!--</div>-->
    <main>
    <div class="container" id="home-content">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="card">
                    <h3 class="card-header">The Normies</h3>
                    <div class="card-block">
                        <p class="card-text">
                            Here at "The Normies", we dedicate ourselves to spreading our dankness to the farthest reaches of the Clash Royale community.
                            As a clan, we try to get the best participation out of all our members.
                            We pride ourselves on our diversity as a clan that allows us to come together to roast on people of all regions.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="card">
                    <h3 class="card-header">What We Do</h3>
                    <div class="card-block">
                        <p class="card-text">
                            We wreck clans... mostly. We have some s*!t players as well, unfortunately. 
                            We require that every player contribute a little to the clan chest every week.
                            Our goal is always to try to get a 10/10 every week. 
                            There are also tournaments hosted from time to time for our loyal clan members. The usurper "Pina" is in exile.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <br/><br/>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-12">
                <div class="jumbotron">
                    <h1 class="display-3">Our Fearless Leader</h1>
                    <hr class="my-2">
                    <div id="leader-home">
                        <p><%= playerName %></p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    </main>
    <footer>
        <div class="container-fluid">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-5">
                    Join Us On<br/>
                    <a href="https://twitter.com/CR_Normies"><img src="./media/footer/twitter.png" alt="twitter"></a>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-5">
                    <p>Made by Sir Doge. Pls give doge coins.<p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>
    <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.2.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script>
        $(document).ready(function(){
            $.getJSON('/files/media/home')
            .done(function(data){
                var i = 0;
                $.each(data, function(key, val){
                    if(i==0){
                        $('#bannerInner').append('<div class="carousel-item active"><img class="d-block w-100 img-fluid" alt="home page background" src="' + val.name + '">');
                    }
                    else{
                        $('#bannerInner').append('<div class="carousel-item"><img class="d-block w-100 img-fluid" alt="home page background" src="' + val.name + '">');
                    }
                    i += 1;
                });
            });
        });
    </script>
</html>